item.description:
For those photogs in our group who love nature photography this is an event you will not want to miss...

Its going to be a private showing of Still Life Nature Photographer Terry Walker's portfolio. He'll show you each image in his portfolio and you'll get the opportunity to chat with him about them... this really is an exciting chance to meet and speak with a professional nature Photographer who is selling his work as fine art. He'll be showcasing his amazing still life nature images and open to your questions about shooting nature. Please visit Terry Walker's website at http://www.terrywalke... to get an idea of some of the wonderful images you will be seeing...

This is a special event, so seating is limited to 10 people so RSVP - ASAP!! Please bring a $5.00 donation at the door the day of the event.

Donna
